graphToNodeGraph(DirectedGraph, String[]) - Static method in class edu.missouri.bayesianConstructor.Main
Deprecated.
since version 0.05 (2016-03-20). A graph of nodes serves no other purpose than to create a edu.ucla.belief.BeliefNetwork; however, the graphs returned by this function are not fully supported by BeliefNetwork (Edges do not get updated properly). Use Main.graphToNetwork(DirectedGraph, String[]) for this purpose instead.
